Requirements Are...
-------------------

1) ANY Classic AMIGA with a minimum of 2MB of mixed memory, (a stock A1200).
2) Extra Floppy drive or optional HDD.
3) Standard OS2.0x to 3.9x.
4) WinUAE 1.5.3 or greater as an alternative.
5) Numbers 7) and 8) are NOT required for the default Audio Generator mode.
6) Workbench MUST be in at least 16 Colours AND 640x200 resolution minimum.

Optional...
-----------

7) ~Project6~ from ~TestGear2.lha~ in the ~docs/hard~ drawer of AMINET.
8) ~WinUAE-ADC.lha~ in the ~docs/hard~ drawer of AMINET.

