                         Audio Frequency Test Set.
                         -------------------------

I decided to release this AS IS because I have decided to change the
hardware from the WinUAE-ADC.lha and Parallel Port ADCs to the Arduino,
(Diecimila in my case), Development Board or newer. This board can be
made to work from USB or RS232 SERIAL ports so that it will suit both
Classic AMIGAs AND WinUAE with only a very SIMPLE home built addition.

It would be nice for some feedback from yourselves just to see what you
think of this idea.

You will notice SINAD in the DEMO as I intended this as a test set for the
PMR/LMR industry.

For the FULL DEMO MODE press 'Alt Shift D' simultaneously and the Window
will expand to full size to allow a hardware DEMO to show.

If you leave it to do its thing it should default to an Audio Function
Generator ONLY which is FULLY functional and finished.

The ACE Basic source code is issued as GPL for the Sweeper-HW in this
uplpoad.

